longBusinessSummary: Metemtur Yatirim Enerji Turizm ve Insaat Anonim Sirketi operates a holiday village in Bodrum Gümbet, Turkey. The company is involved in the construction and sale of Fugayaz Gündogan houses; and generation and sale of electricity through solar power plants. Metemtur Yatirim Enerji Turizm ve Insaat Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
